@startuml frame-lifecycle
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #666
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #F8F8F8

title Frame Lifecycle - Command-Based Rendering

participant "Application" as App
participant "Renderer" as Renderer
participant "CommandRecorder" as Cmd
participant "SwapChain" as Swap
participant "Queue" as Queue
participant "GPU" as GPU

== Frame N Start ==
App -> Renderer: BeginFrame()
activate Renderer

Renderer -> Swap: AcquireNextImage()
activate Swap
Swap -> Swap: Wait for available
Swap --> Renderer: Backbuffer[N]
deactivate Swap

Renderer -> Renderer: Wait(Fence[N-2])
note right: Triple buffering:\nWait for frame N-2

Renderer -> Renderer: GetCommandRecorder()
Renderer -> Cmd: Begin()
activate Cmd

Renderer --> App: CommandRecorder*
deactivate Renderer

== Command Recording ==
App -> Cmd: BeginRenderPass(nullptr)
note right: nullptr = backbuffer
Cmd -> Cmd: Set RenderPass state

App -> Cmd: RenderScene(scene)
activate Cmd
Cmd -> Cmd: SetPipeline()
Cmd -> Cmd: SetBindGroups()
Cmd -> Cmd: Draw calls...
deactivate Cmd

App -> Cmd: EndRenderPass()
note right: **Explicit end required**
Cmd -> Cmd: Close RenderPass

alt Multi-pass Rendering
    App -> Cmd: BeginRenderPass(shadowMap)
    App -> Cmd: RenderShadows()
    App -> Cmd: EndRenderPass()
    
    App -> Cmd: BeginRenderPass(nullptr)
    App -> Cmd: RenderMain()
    App -> Cmd: EndRenderPass()
end

== Frame Submission ==
App -> Renderer: EndFrame(cmd)
activate Renderer

Renderer -> Cmd: Finish()
Cmd -> Cmd: Validate state
note right: Error if RenderPass\nstill active
Cmd --> Renderer: CommandBuffer
deactivate Cmd

Renderer -> Queue: Submit(CommandBuffer, Fence[N])
activate Queue
Queue -> GPU: Execute Commands
activate GPU

Renderer -> Swap: Present()
note left: Schedule presentation

Renderer -> Renderer: Signal(Fence[N])

Renderer --> App: Frame Complete
deactivate Renderer

== Parallel Execution ==
GPU -> GPU: Process Frame N
note right: Vertex Processing\nRasterization\nFragment Shading

App -> App: Prepare Frame N+1
note left: CPU can prepare\nnext frame

Queue --> GPU: Complete
deactivate GPU
GPU -> GPU: Display Frame N-1
deactivate Queue

== Error Cases ==
group Error: Unfinished RenderPass
    App -> Renderer: EndFrame(cmd)
    Renderer -> Cmd: Finish()
    Cmd --> Renderer: ERROR: RenderPass active
    Renderer --> App: Exception
end

group Error: Missing EndRenderPass
    App -> Cmd: BeginRenderPass()
    App -> Cmd: Draw()
    App -> Cmd: BeginRenderPass()
    Cmd --> App: ERROR: Previous pass not ended
end

@enduml